</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="20BC6569FFD529797048E33C3AD5FAC4" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="681936E2FFD529797048E33C3AD5FAC4" blockId="2.[136,1059,1090,1372]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">
<materialsCitation id="D8CE3CBFFFD529797048E33C3AD3FBE4" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">
Two probable ♂ 
<typeStatus id="B71D8840FFD529797090E33C3B19FBC3" box="[717,810,1092,1116]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">syntypes</typeStatus>
(box 28), placed in the collection as 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797302E31C3AD3FBE4" authority="(Serville, 1839)" authorityName="R. Roy" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" box="[351,736,1123,1147]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Paramantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasina">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797302E31C3A00FBE4" box="[351,563,1124,1147]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">Paramantis prasina</emphasis>
(Serville, 1839)
</taxonomicName>
</materialsCitation>
. Both match the measurement given in the description and each has two handwritten labels: &quot;♂ Ile Bourbon M. H. de Saussure&quot; and &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD5297973A4E3DB3AF3FB24" authorityName="Saussure" authorityYear="1869" box="[505,704,1187,1211]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Mantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="emortualis">Mantis emortualis</taxonomicName>
♂ type Sauss.&quot; (red paper). In addition, one of them bears a label &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797037E3BB3B8EFB44" authority="Serv. Det Beier" authorityName="Serv. Det Beier" box="[618,957,1219,1243]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Mantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasina">Mantis prasina Serv. Det Beier</taxonomicName>
&quot; and the other &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD52979737CE39B3AAEFB63" authority="(Serv.) R. Roy" authorityName="R. Roy" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" box="[289,669,1251,1276]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Paramantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasina">Paramantis prasina (Serv.) R. Roy</taxonomicName>
det. 1974&quot;, both handwritten. The original description gives the type locality as “Patria?” rather than the more precise provenance on the labels. 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD52979700FE25C3ADFFAA4" authorityName="Saussure" authorityYear="1869" box="[594,748,1315,1339]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Mantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="emortualis">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD52979700FE25C3ADFFAA4" box="[594,748,1315,1339]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">M. emortualis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is now considered a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797307E23C3AECFAC4" authority="(Serville, 1839)" authorityName="R. Roy" baseAuthorityName="Serville" baseAuthorityYear="1839" box="[346,735,1347,1371]" class="Insecta" family="Mantidae" genus="Paramantis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="prasina">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797307E23C3A1CFAC4" box="[346,559,1348,1371]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">Paramantis prasina</emphasis>
(Serville, 1839)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
